### LISTAR
GET {{baseUrl}}/clientes?page=0&size=100
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### CRIAR
POST {{baseUrl}}/clientes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

