### LISTAR ENDERECOS
GET {{baseUrl}}/clientes/{{clienteId}}/enderecos

### CRIAR ENDERECO
POST {{baseUrl}}/clientes/{{clienteId}}/enderecos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cep": "88000000",
  "estado": "SC",
  "cidade": "Florianopolis",
  "bairro": "Centro",
  "logradouro": "Rua A",
  "numero": "123",
  "tipoEndereco": "ENTREGA",
  "apelido": "Casa"
}

### ATUALIZAR
PUT {{baseUrl}}/clientes/{{clienteId}}/enderecos/{{enderecoId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cep": "88000000",
  "estado": "SC",
  "cidade": "Florianopolis",
  "bairro": "Centro",
  "logradouro": "Rua B",
  "numero": "456",
  "tipoEndereco": "ENTREGA",
  "apelido": "Casa Edit"
}

### DELETE
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/clientes/{{clienteId}}/enderecos/{{enderecoId}}